Directions:
Take Interstate 10 (I-10) east to AZ-287 West/Florence Blvd in Casa Grande. Take exit 194 from I-10 E.  Turn west onto AZ-287/Florence Blvd.  Just Past S. Henness Road,  Banner Casa Grande Medical Center will be on the Right (North) side of the road.  Turn North in to Banner Casa Grande Medical Center’s parking lot.  The 1780 medical building is connected to the hospital, and is located on the westside of the main hospital, ground floor in suite 108.  

Tome la carretera interestatal 10 (I-10) hacia el este hasta AZ-287 West / Florence Blvd en Casa Grande. Tome la salida 194 de la I-10 E. Gire hacia el oeste en AZ-287 / Florence Blvd. Justo después de S. Henness Road, el Centro Médico Banner Casa Grande estará en el lado derecho (norte) de la carretera. Gire hacia el norte hacia el estacionamiento de Banner Casa Grande Medical Center. El edificio médico 1780 está conectado al hospital y está ubicado en el lado oeste del hospital principal, en la planta baja de la suite 108.

Site: Emory University Georgia Clinical Research Center
Notes: Formerly HPO Emory Univ CRN
Scheduling Instructions:
Thank you, someone from Emory Healthcare will be contacting you to schedule your All of Us Research Program enrollment appointment.

Gracias, agluien de Emory Healthcare se comunicará con usted para programar su cita de registración con el Programa Científico All of Us.
Directions:
GCRC (formerly CRN):

We are located in Emory Hospital at 1364 Clifton Rd, Ground Floor, Atlanta, GA 30322. Valet is available at the Emory Hospital ER valet entrance and self-parking is located off of Lowergate Drive. We will validate your parking ticket for this visit.

Emory Hospital ER Valet entrance

  • Walk in and go straight, make a left turn and walk down the long hallway toward the G elevators
  • Take the elevator to the Ground floor
  • Once you exit the elevator, turn right and walk past the cafeteria and the Asbury Express Café.
  • Please enter through the metal double doors on the right (HG01 - HG Medical Unit).
  • The All of Us visit room will be the first door on your left, room #HG-03.

Self-Parking

  • Follow the signs on the bridge to walk towards the hospital entrance
  • Once in the main hospital lobby make a left turn and walk down the long hallway toward the G elevators
  • Take the elevator to the Ground floor
  • Once you exit the elevator, turn right and walk past the cafeteria and the Asbury Express Café.
  • Please enter through the metal double doors on the right (HG01 - HG Medical Unit).
  • The All of Us visit room will be the first door on your left, room #HG-03.

If you get turned around, please call the Coordinator when you arrive and we will meet you outside of the cafeteria, 404-712-3501 or 404-712-7632.

We are looking forward to seeing you.

Scheduling Instructions:
Thank you, someone from Emory Healthcare will be contacting you to schedule your All of Us Research Program enrollment appointment.

Gracias, agluien de Emory Healthcare se comunicará con usted para programar su cita de registración con el Programa Científico All of Us.
Directions:
Cardiology:

We are located in Emory Clinic Building A 1365 Clifton Rd Atlanta, GA 30322 on the Tunnel level. Valet and self-parking are both located off of Lowergate Drive. We will validate your parking ticket for this visit.

Valet Parking

  • Once you have valeted your car, please go through the Emory Clinic Building A entrance
  • Turn right as if heading towards the cardiology clinic, you will pass a gift shop on your left
  • To the right of the cardiology clinic are elevators, please take one of the elevators down to the tunnel level (T).
  • Follow the signs for "Cardiac Imaging"
  • Once at Cardiac Imaging, Turn left. There is a small All of Us sign with a blue arrow attached to the wall

Self-Parking

  • Park at Lowergate East
  • Take the elevator to the 2nd floor
  • Follow the ramp/bridge to Emory Clinic A elevators and take it to floor 1.
  • Turn left and walk towards the cardiology clinic, you will pass a gift shop on your left
  • To the right of the cardiology clinic are elevators, please take one of the elevators down to the tunnel level (T).
  • Follow the signs for "Cardiac Imaging"
  • Once at Cardiac Imaging, Turn left. There is a small All of Us sign with a blue arrow attached to the wall

If you have any problems finding us, please call 404-778-0594 and we will come meet you and walk you to our site. We look forward to seeing you.

Site: Emory University - Clinic at West Ponce
Google Group Name: HPO Emory Univ Clinic West Ponce
Directions:
West Ponce:

We are located at The Emory Clinic on West Ponce at 158 W Ponce de Leon Ave, Decatur, GA 30030 between the old Thumbs Up Diner and DeKalb History Center Museum.

There is an entrance to the One West Court parking deck next to us. Please use this to self-park. We will validate your parking for one hour and 20 minutes.

Once you have parked, exit the parking deck and take a left turn, and walk down the street to our clinic. You will see a small blue and white sign that says “Emory Clinic.” If you have a clinic appointment, check in with the receptionist. If you do not have a clinic appointment, enter the double glass doors and take a right turn. Enter the double doors with All of Us Research Program signage. You will not need to check in with the receptionist.

Please let us know if you have any questions. We are looking forward to seeing you.
Physical Location Name: The Emory Clinic at West Ponce
